 StudyNotes App

A simple and efficient web-based note-taking application designed for students to quickly create, edit, and manage study notes. The app mimics digital sticky notes with color coding and stores data locally for offline access.

---

 Features

-  Add new study notes
-  Edit notes in real-time
-  Delete notes
-  Color-coded notes for better organization
-  Local storage (data persists after refresh)
-  Timestamp for each note

---

 Technologies Used

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript (LocalStorage)

---

 How to Run

1. Download or clone this repository
2. Open "index.html" in any browser

